test_large_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4] == [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
  Right contains one more item: 5
  Full diff:
  - [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
  ?            ---
  + [1, 2, 3, 4]
test_even_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4] == [2, 4, 6, 8, 10]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 2
  Right contains one more item: 10
  Full diff:
  - [2, 4, 6, 8, 10]
  + [1, 2, 3, 4]
